item.title: Nrs3server v4 help
item.dc:creator: @TimeRS3 TimeRS3
item.description:
@TimeRS3 wrote:

zenith cache will not work that is a 667/725 your looking at v4 is a 718/***

look through cache archive post i made either on here or r-s and the error is most likely appearing because you have not set the client and source sub = 3 also it could be the fact that the opcodes are not right for the cache although all version of cache before 725 should work as long as they are 718/***.
